---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research - Udbhav Tripathi">
	<div class="container">
		<h1>Research</h1>
		
		<section class="research-project">
			<h2>Scientific Foundation Models (SciFM)</h2>
			<p>
				My research in Scientific Foundation Models focuses on developing foundational AI models specifically designed 
				for scientific applications. This work involves creating large-scale models that can understand and generate 
				scientific content, solve complex mathematical problems, and assist in scientific discovery. Key areas include:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Development of pre-trained models for scientific data</li>
				<li>Integration of physical constraints in neural architectures</li>
				<li>Transfer learning for scientific applications</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="research-project">
			<h2>Scientific Machine Learning (SciML)</h2>
			<p>
				In SciML, my work focuses on combining traditional scientific computing methods with modern machine learning 
				approaches. This includes:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Neural networks for solving partial differential equations</li>
				<li>Physics-informed machine learning models</li>
				<li>Data-driven discovery of physical systems</li>
				<li>Optimization techniques for scientific computing</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="research-project">
			<h2>Large Language Models (LLM)</h2>
			<p>
				My research in LLMs focuses on their application in scientific domains. This includes:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Scientific text understanding and generation</li>
				<li>Code generation for scientific computing</li>
				<li>Mathematical reasoning and problem-solving</li>
				<li>Integration of domain knowledge in language models</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="research-project">
			<h2>3D Geometry Problems</h2>
			<p>
				In the field of 3D geometry, my research focuses on:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Deep learning for 3D shape analysis</li>
				<li>Geometric deep learning</li>
				<li>Point cloud processing and analysis</li>
				<li>3D reconstruction and understanding</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>

